# apps/backend/src/modules/whatsapp/

## Responsibility
Manages WhatsApp channel records, channel metadata, badges, and channel-specific settings.

## Design
Service-driven CRUD module with UUID validation, app scoping, and conflict checks so a phone number cannot belong to multiple apps.

## Flow
Routes list/detail/update/create channels, map quality/tier data for the UI, and store metadata such as default chatbot/flow/team/agent assignments.

## Integration
Uses Prisma, app-id resolution, S3 for badge uploads, inbox/channel config, and downstream automation defaults for chatbot/flow routing.

